T1  - Newcomer Identification: Trends, Antecedents, Moderators, and Consequences
AU  - Zhu, Jing
AU  - Tatachari, Srinivasan
AU  - Chattopadhyay, Prithviraj
Y1  - 2016/04/25
PY  - 2016
DA  - 2017/06/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amj.2015.0466
